summary: Killing Eve, S01E02 If there’s a hunt for a mysterious globe-trotting assassin you can be pretty sure there’ll be a crazy wall....
caption:
Killing Eve, S01E02

If there’s a hunt for a mysterious globe-trotting assassin you can be pretty sure there’ll be a crazy wall. And, yes, here we are. “What is this?” exclaims Eve upon seeing it. Unfortunately the answer is not, “It’s our crazy wall!”

I’ve lightened this image because, like every modern TV drama, this show is set in a future world in which every home, office, school… in fact every interior space, is suffering from the global shortage of lightbulbs.
